<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
	<h1>Fast packet processing. No proprietary hardware required.</h1>
<p>DPDK is an open source framework for fast packet processing on standard hardware. It runs in cloud infrastructure, telecom networks, financial exchanges, particle accelerators, and radio telescopes. Most of your traffic already runs through it. Start by reviewing a patch, no account or setup required.</p>
</div>



<a class="nectar-button medium regular accent-color  regular-button"  role="button" style="margin-top: 25px; margin-right: 25px; "  href="/review-your-first-patch/" data-color-override="false" data-hover-color-override="false" data-hover-text-color-override="#fff"><span>Review Your First Patch</span></a><a class="nectar-button medium regular accent-color  regular-button"  role="button" style="margin-right: 25px; color: #252525; background-color: #FFFFFF;"  href="/contribute-your-first-patch/" data-color-override="#FFFFFF" data-hover-color-override="false" data-hover-text-color-override="#fff"><span>Contribute Your First Patch</span></a><a class="nectar-button medium regular accent-color  regular-button"  role="button" style="color: #252525; background-color: #FFFFFF;"  href="https://github.com/DPDK/dpdk" data-color-override="#FFFFFF" data-hover-color-override="false" data-hover-text-color-override="#fff"><span>Get the Code</span></a>
			</div> 
		</div>
	</div> 

	<div style="" class="vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column column_container vc_column_container col padding-2-percent inherit_tablet inherit_phone " data-using-bg="true" data-border-radius="15px" data-padding-pos="all" data-has-bg-color="true" data-bg-color="#FFFFFF" data-bg-opacity="1" data-animation="" data-delay="0" >
