<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
	<p>VIDEOS ARE LIVE</p>
<h3>DPDK Summit 2026</h3>
<p>29 sessions from Stockholm. New recordings published every week through the summer.</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLo97Rhbj4ceL54ZJHxxcpZljm-Wlx3g4W&amp;si=TfJb-IR0D2cgLNKi">Browse sessions →</a></strong></p>
</div>




